{"tid":2415510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新年行夜市食香腸串燒　2歲女童失足跌倒竹籤刺穿鼻","createTime":"2021-02-20T10:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T00:57:50.000Z","uid":271829,"like":189,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":123,"replies":[{"pid":"af7e14c2def092c613e9a7539602e8ee402e6728","tid":2415510,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/stick_thumb_20210220_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2Fstick_thumb_20210220_S_600.jpg&h=50c4686e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 新年行夜市食香腸串燒，2歲女童失足跌倒竹籤刺穿鼻。<br />\n<br />\n小朋友邊行邊進食隨時發生可怕意外。內地一名2歲女童與家人吃過團年飯後去逛夜市，未料在食烤香腸時不慎摔倒，香腸的竹籤直插鼻孔並刺穿鼻翼，畫面恐怖，家人隨即帶她求醫，幸好送院治療後目前已無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內地媒體報道，事發在上周六（13日），貴州黔南州一名2歲女童跟父母到外公、外婆家拜年並吃團年飯，飯後全家人去逛夜市，路過燒烤攤檔時，女童的母親買了一些串燒給家人享用，亦買了一根烤香腸給女兒。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到母親轉身時，女童因無人看管，不慎從台階摔下，串著香腸的竹籤更插入鼻孔，並貫穿鼻翼，女童當場痛得哇哇大哭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/1cad192da36f494483f01f8d2fb8aa17_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2F1cad192da36f494483f01f8d2fb8aa17_600.jpeg&h=dc6a652b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/89cb72149c05490a87c446ef4f8a387b_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2F89cb72149c05490a87c446ef4f8a387b_600.jpeg&h=a7d6f287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女童家長隨即駕車送她到醫院，剛好遇上公安交通管理局警員打擊酒後駕駛，由於擔心城區街道車流較高，會耽誤車程，於是家長告訴警員車上有孩子受傷，請求幫忙開路。警員了解情況後，立即駕駛警車開路，在指揮中心擬定路線下，不用5分鐘就將女童送到醫院。<br />\n<br />\n到達醫院後，警員將女童抱在懷內，從門口一路送進急症室電梯，全程陪同女童及其父母直到治療結束。幸好送院及時，女童目前已無大礙。女童家長向幾名警員致謝，而警員在離開前，再次叮囑女童父母今後要關注好孩子的安全。"},{"pid":"2d2f730c274311f6a6f007f56f76d446eeb35536","tid":2415510,"uid":2914,"like":140,"dislike":0,"score":140,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"成日行過啲小食鋪我都好驚會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595b008f5d2e479fd77eb9432a00edea4ff514f4","tid":2415510,"uid":202051,"like":196,"dislike":1,"score":195,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慘 我細個都有幻想過呢啲意外"},{"pid":"b88c0ad39906643fb3c777141fc3be452ab08b5e","tid":2415510,"uid":256215,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"講明意外，咁驚食飯同時呼吸都可以死人"},{"pid":"f2e300246de76ebdf8a8e932ebe71f06076e66b8","tid":2415510,"uid":44454,"like":244,"dislike":2,"score":242,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"所以逢係竹籤嘢我都打橫食"},{"pid":"22eda7fbd77e35e8601cc615fe664950d5550905","tid":2415510,"uid":62950,"like":143,"dislike":3,"score":140,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"算好彩  插鼻唔係插眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36792091fe962e0e1f15b376466b51339448e723","tid":2415510,"uid":120627,"like":20,"dislike":95,"score":-75,"quote":{"pid":"f2e300246de76ebdf8a8e932ebe71f06076e66b8","tid":2415510,"uid":44454,"like":244,"dislike":2,"score":242,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"所以逢係竹籤嘢我都打橫食"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:16:55.000Z","msg":"打橫人地一撞你隻手踭你個口會多左個窿"},{"pid":"7caf8bddf17309ee37e1f3cc83b2526c7a1b007a","tid":2415510,"uid":11301,"like":25,"dislike":8,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"串燒蝗蟲"},{"pid":"eebe1cc37fb8ab5210933f4996608df9f69e4b34","tid":2415510,"uid":44454,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"quote":{"pid":"36792091fe962e0e1f15b376466b51339448e723","tid":2415510,"uid":120627,"like":20,"dislike":95,"score":-75,"quote":{"pid":"f2e300246de76ebdf8a8e932ebe71f06076e66b8","tid":2415510,"uid":44454,"like":244,"dislike":2,"score":242,"citedBy":5