e":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"36792091fe962e0e1f15b376466b51339448e723","tid":2415510,"uid":120627,"like":20,"dislike":95,"score":-75,"quote":{"pid":"f2e300246de76ebdf8a8e932ebe71f06076e66b8","tid":2415510,"uid":44454,"like":244,"dislike":2,"score":242,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"所以逢係竹籤嘢我都打橫食"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:16:55.000Z","msg":"打橫人地一撞你隻手踭你個口會多左個窿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:32:50.000Z","msg":"你個口打橫含撚?"},{"pid":"08f14662a17578c3e05ed1b78fefacbeba86697e","tid":2415510,"uid":84341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af7e14c2def092c613e9a7539602e8ee402e6728","tid":2415510,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/stick_thumb_20210220_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2Fstick_thumb_20210220_S_600.jpg&h=50c4686e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 新年行夜市食香腸串燒，2歲女童失足跌倒竹籤刺穿鼻。<br />\n<br />\n小朋友邊行邊進食隨時發生可怕意外。內地一名2歲女童與家人吃過團年飯後去逛夜市，未料在食烤香腸時不慎摔倒，香腸的竹籤直插鼻孔並刺穿鼻翼，畫面恐怖，家人隨即帶她求醫，幸好送院治療後目前已無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內地媒體報道，事發在上周六（13日），貴州黔南州一名2歲女童跟父母到外公、外婆家拜年並吃團年飯，飯後全家人去逛夜市，路過燒烤攤檔時，女童的母親買了一些串燒給家人享用，亦買了一根烤香腸給女兒。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到母親轉身時，女童因無人看管，不慎從台階摔下，串著香腸的竹籤更插入鼻孔，並貫穿鼻翼，女童當場痛得哇哇大哭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/1cad192da36f494483f01f8d2fb8aa17_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2F1cad192da36f494483f01f8d2fb8aa17_600.jpeg&h=dc6a652b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/89cb72149c05490a87c446ef4f8a387b_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2F89cb72149c05490a87c446ef4f8a387b_600.jpeg&h=a7d6f287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女童家長隨即駕車送她到醫院，剛好遇上公安交通管理局警員打擊酒後駕駛，由於擔心城區街道車流較高，會耽誤車程，於是家長告訴警員車上有孩子受傷，請求幫忙開路。警員了解情況後，立即駕駛警車開路，在指揮中心擬定路線下，不用5分鐘就將女童送到醫院。<br />\n<br />\n到達醫院後，警員將女童抱在懷內，從門口一路送進急症室電梯，全程陪同女童及其父母直到治療結束。幸好送院及時，女童目前已無大礙。女童家長向幾名警員致謝，而警員在離開前，再次叮囑女童父母今後要關注好孩子的安全。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"好心咁細個就唔好俾佢揸住竹籤啦"},{"pid":"21dc54078cd0565148c315c176f1cc13e16a1f5a","tid":2415510,"uid":117237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4063b295c971dddab3930c9e8f7235dd47aaf614","tid":2415510,"uid":297045,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2e300246de76ebdf8a8e932ebe71f06076e66b8","tid":2415510,"uid":44454,"like":244,"dislike":2,"score":242,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"所以逢係竹籤嘢我都打橫食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"我寧願唔食依d街邊小食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食都食得咁辛苦, 食黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"食小食都可以食到辛苦<br />\n<br />\n有兩種人<br />\n1）弱智<br />\n2）話比人地聽我好離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e9635431ed14ad1794938f5d09087c286483c4","tid":2415510,"uid":91471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26fdd1370c911fb3d80fb16e63da6ade66d0aa94","tid":2415510,"uid":56206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"22eda7fbd77e35e8601cc615fe664950d5550905","tid":2415510,"uid":62950,"like":143,"dislike":3,"score":140,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"算好彩  插鼻唔係插眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"Another <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T1