me":"2021-02-20T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"插咗入去先係好彩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"插入去好似可以直接入腦<br />\n整木乃伊都係係個鼻到將個腦「筆」出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b8408af0c4b2f735f7161850ead29456215b92","tid":2415510,"uid":387588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"由細到大老母都有教唔好行住食，仲有教飲食場所唔可以跑，好彩"},{"pid":"feb6693b2a621c2116770a42730e7cb5a65b7405","tid":2415510,"uid":271981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af7e14c2def092c613e9a7539602e8ee402e6728","tid":2415510,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/stick_thumb_20210220_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2Fstick_thumb_20210220_S_600.jpg&h=50c4686e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 新年行夜市食香腸串燒，2歲女童失足跌倒竹籤刺穿鼻。<br />\n<br />\n小朋友邊行邊進食隨時發生可怕意外。內地一名2歲女童與家人吃過團年飯後去逛夜市，未料在食烤香腸時不慎摔倒，香腸的竹籤直插鼻孔並刺穿鼻翼，畫面恐怖，家人隨即帶她求醫，幸好送院治療後目前已無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內地媒體報道，事發在上周六（13日），貴州黔南州一名2歲女童跟父母到外公、外婆家拜年並吃團年飯，飯後全家人去逛夜市，路過燒烤攤檔時，女童的母親買了一些串燒給家人享用，亦買了一根烤香腸給女兒。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到母親轉身時，女童因無人看管，不慎從台階摔下，串著香腸的竹籤更插入鼻孔，並貫穿鼻翼，女童當場痛得哇哇大哭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/1cad192da36f494483f01f8d2fb8aa17_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2F1cad192da36f494483f01f8d2fb8aa17_600.jpeg&h=dc6a652b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2880000/2882292/89cb72149c05490a87c446ef4f8a387b_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2880000%2F2882292%2F89cb72149c05490a87c446ef4f8a387b_600.jpeg&h=a7d6f287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女童家長隨即駕車送她到醫院，剛好遇上公安交通管理局警員打擊酒後駕駛，由於擔心城區街道車流較高，會耽誤車程，於是家長告訴警員車上有孩子受傷，請求幫忙開路。警員了解情況後，立即駕駛警車開路，在指揮中心擬定路線下，不用5分鐘就將女童送到醫院。<br />\n<br />\n到達醫院後，警員將女童抱在懷內，從門口一路送進急症室電梯，全程陪同女童及其父母直到治療結束。幸好送院及時，女童目前已無大礙。女童家長向幾名警員致謝，而警員在離開前，再次叮囑女童父母今後要關注好孩子的安全。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:18:48.000Z","msg":"睇標題估國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又中"},{"pid":"46078e1692d745f01ffedb8ed209a3028760fef5","tid":2415510,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"抵啦<br />\n啲支那豬湊仔亂鳩咁嚟"},{"pid":"2fd6626e78c210e2663cf06001c189771e02220f","tid":2415510,"uid":32691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"咁細個就穿鼻打環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02586d13d0556465d0d620b789d2486e61827c9a","tid":2415510,"uid":47647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be73bf46cf9a748a2ac374caef683c4d9cf283dc","tid":2415510,"uid":104454,"like":90,"dislike":3,"score":87,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:20:28.000Z","msg":"免費鼻環穿洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:31:37.000Z","msg":"免費打洞 得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cd014036a550ff594baf8341af9beed311c7af","tid":2415510,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"咁細個穿鼻窿"},{"pid":"99960a183f5aea6737a60fbda7595ee1d1c66dde","tid":2415510,"uid":56989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"夠哂cyberpunk"},{"pid":"09e53721ec74238003694a4e9aa9faeb083df75b","tid":2415510,"uid":4440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"鼻哥窿-1"},{"pid":"c35dd1235bb905c1012e2f7ac5